%N A396276 Triangle T(n,k), n >= 0, 0 <= k <= (3^n-1)/2, read by rows, where T(n,k) = [x^k] (F_n(x)/x)^(1/2) and F_n(x) is the n-th iteration of x*(1 + x)^2.
%H A396276 Seiichi Manyama, <a href="/A396276/b396276.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..4924</a> (rows 0..8)
%F A396276 (F_n(x)/x)^(1/2) = Product_{j=0..n-1} (1 + F_j(x)).
%F A396276 T(n,k) = Sum_{0 = x_0 <= x_1 <= ... <= x_{n-1} <= x_n = k} Product_{j=0..n-1} binomial(2*x_j + 1,x_{j+1} - x_j).
%e A396276 F_0(x) = x.
%e A396276 F_1(x) = x + 2*x^2 + x^3.
%e A396276 F_2(x) = x + 4*x^2 + 10*x^3 + 18*x^4 + 23*x^5 + 22*x^6 + 15*x^7 + 6*x^8 + x^9.
%e A396276 F_3(x) = x + 6*x^2 + 27*x^3 + 102*x^4 + 333*x^5 + 960*x^6 + 2472*x^7 + ...  + x^27.
%e A396276 Triangle begins:
%e A396276   1;
%e A396276   1, 1;
%e A396276   1, 2, 3,  3,  1;
%e A396276   1, 3, 9, 24, 54, 102, 156, 192, 189, 147, 87, 36, 9, 1;
%e A396276   ...
